   <Ritual>
      <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
         <ab>Y33.4 Var. a (mss. 40, 88, 400, 410 (sec.m.), 2005, 2007, 2101, 2106, 2109, 4010, 4025, 4030a, 4055, 4060, 4063, 5020):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            ... <em>nazdištąm drujəm</em>. hōm ud urwarām kōftan ud hāwan škāftan tā wacist sar</ab>  
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "At ... <em>nazdištąm drujəm</em>, he should strike the <em>hōm</em> and <em>urwarām</em> and hit the <em>hāwan</em>.</ab>
         <ab>Y33.4 Var. b (mss. 15, 2030 (sec.m.), 2101, 2104):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            ... <em>nazdištąm drujəm</em>. ēn gyāg hōm ud urwarām kōftan ud hāwan škāftan ud zōhr andar kardan</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "At ... <em>nazdištąm drujəm</em>, he should strike the <em>hōm</em> and <em>urwarām</em>, hit the <em>hāwan</em> and put <em>zōhr</em> in it."</ab>
         <ab>Y33.4 Var. c (mss. 82, 4000, 4020, 4040, 4050, 4161 (sec.m.), 4162):</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            ... <em>nazdištąm drujəm</em>. ēn gyāg hōm ud urwarām kōftan</ab>
         <ab class="ab_indent">
            "At ... <em>nazdištąm drujəm</em>, he should strike the <em>hōm</em> and <em>urwarām</em>."</ab>
      </Nerangs>
